Invocation Name: prime numbers
des: Ask Prime Numbers for all of your prime number needs! Calculate a specific prime number or determine whether a number is prime! For example, ask Prime Numbers: "Is 443 prime?" or "What is the 932nd prime number?" and Prime Numbers will tell you!
